THESE THINGS GO;

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:25.000
IT'S A HORROR FLICK.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.000
YOU THINK THEY'RE
DEAD... BUT ARE THEY?

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
YOU JUST CAN'T GET RID
OF THEM THAT EASILY.

